# Archived Indicators

This folder contains indicators that have been retired from active use.

## Archive Policy
- Indicators replaced by better versions
- Indicators with duplicate functionality
- Indicators with negative impact on performance

## Archive Contents
- Original code
- Date archived
- Reason for archiving
- Replacement indicator (if applicable)

## Format
Each archived indicator should be saved as:
`archived/indicators/[indicator_name]_v[X.X.X]_archived_[YYYY-MM-DD].py`

